Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:48.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:50.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because your soul is what you were BORN TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:54.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たとえ今まで生きるstrategy 夢失っても　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:55.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(It's time now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:57.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ハンドルを切って暴れ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:23:00.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夢のまま突き進め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:02.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬のない人生に挑むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:05.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忍のない感情を抱くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:07.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覚悟決めて行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:10.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分自身をbreak away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:15.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全てを奪われる運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:17.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何を信じて生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:22.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ask yourself, the way there's nothing to live or die for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:25.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過去も傷も恐れるなら
